data.title: Dalhalla
data.meta_description: A closed limestone quarry outside the town of Rättvik in the Swedish boreal forest was turned into an outdoor arena for cultural events such as operas and concerts. Dimensions of the quarry: 400m x 175m x 55m Pictures from: http://www.mynewsdesk.com/se/pressroom/dalhalla/image/view/dalhalla-6404 http://www.mynewsdesk.com/se/pressroom/dalhalla/image/view/dalhalla-6403
data.text:
A closed limestone quarry outside the town of Rättvik in the Swedish boreal forest was turned into an outdoor arena for cultural events such as operas and concerts.

Dimensions of the quarry: 400m x 175m x 55m
